{
  "texts": [
    "• We perform an extensive set of experiments on transformer-based LLMs (RoBERTa, GPT-2, Gemma-2B, and LLaMA-3-8B) on various NLU and NLG tasks and compare them with existing baselines.",
    "On average, the proposed techniques perform better.",
    "We show that LoRMA shows faster convergence.",
    "Via various ablation studies, we demonstrate the benefits of the approach and analyze the effect of rank, weight matrix choice, and correlation between weight updates of LoRA and LoRMA.",
    "We release our code at https: //github.com/Exploration-Lab/LoRMA."
  ]
}